headline: 1 Services Stock to Own for Decades and 2 Facing Challenges
summary: Business services providers thrive by solving complex operational challenges for their clients, allowing them to focus on their secret sauce. These firms have helped their customers unlock huge efficiencies, so it’s no surprise the industry has posted a 13.1% gain over the past six months, nearly mirrorring the S&P 500.
